I don't know.

40
00:08:50,615 --> 00:08:55,143
- 你要去血腥营地，对吧？
- 劳夫，该死的，滚开
-You're going to Camp Blood, ain't you?
-Goddamn it, Ralph, get out of here!

41
00:08:55,253 --> 00:08:58,518
