It's got a death curse!

44
00:09:07,098 --> 00:09:09,259
这小子真是个末日先知，对吧？
He's a real prophet of doom, ain't he?

45
00:09:10,902 --> 00:09:12,096
上车吧，小姐
Climb up, miss.

46
00:09:31,089 --> 00:09:34,650
他的胡言乱语让你的老板伤透脑筋
He's causing problems enough
for your boss with all that talk.

47
00:09:37,061 --> 00:09:39,052
这家伙真是个讨厌鬼
Goddamn nuisance.

48
00:10:03,855 --> 00:10:06,881
- 他有没有跟你说了些什么？
- 谁？
-He tell you anything?
-Who?

49
00:10:06,991 --> 00:10:09,824
你老板，史帝夫克斯帝
Your boss. Steve Christy.

50
00:10:09,927 --> 00:10:12,794
他说我要帮50个小孩和十个工作人员烧菜
I'll be cooking for 50 kids and 10 staff.

51
00:10:13,731 --> 00:10:16,632
来这里露营的多半是贫民区的小孩
-Campers will mostly be inner-city children.
-No, I mean about what happened.

52
00:10:16,734 --> 00:10:18,759
不，我说的是当年发生的事

53
00:10:22,140 --> 00:10:23,368
没有
No.

54
00:10:29,013 --> 00:10:32,312
你一定有事瞒着我
Come on. There's something
you're not telling me.

55
00:10:34,285 --> 00:10:36,480
我劝你现在就辞职
-Quit. Quit now.
-Quit? Why would I want to quit?

56
00:10:36,587 --> 00:10:39,681
辞职？为什么？

57
00:10:40,425 --> 00:10:42,689
水晶湖营地被诅咒了
Camp Crystal Lake is jinxed!

58
00:10:42,794 --> 00:10:45,285
连你也说这种话
Terrific. Not you too. You sound
like your crazy friend back there.

59
00:10:45,396 --> 00:10:47,455
你和刚刚那个疯子劳夫差不多嘛

60
00:10:47,565 --> 00:10:50,261
也许吧
克斯帝有没有告诉你
Well, maybe. Did Christy tell you about
the two kids murdered in '58?

61
00:10:50,368 --> 00:10:53,269
58年那两个年轻人被杀的事？

62
00:10:53,371 --> 00:10:58,434
57年那个男孩淹死的事？
还有当年那些火灾？
Boy drowning in '57? A bunch of fires?

63
00:10:58,543 --> 00:11:00,636
警方根本查不出是谁干的好事
Nobody knows who did any of them.

64
00:11:00,878 --> 00:11:05,440
