67
00:11:08,886 --> 00:11:14,051
他用了一整年整修那个地方，
至少花了两万五千元
He's been up there a year fixing up that
place. Must have dropped $25,000.

68
00:11:14,158 --> 00:11:17,525
他这是何苦？你去问问别人就知道
And for what? Ask anybody.

69
00:11:18,629 --> 00:11:22,190
- 辞职吧！
- 我不能
-Quit!
-I can't.

70
00:11:22,934 --> 00:11:26,233
你们这些傻小孩自以为无所不知
Dumb kids. Know-it-alls.

71
00:11:26,337 --> 00:11:29,329
就像我的┡一样，脑袋里都装石头
Just like my nieces. Heads full of rocks.

72
00:11:30,041 --> 00:11:32,532
你真是个典型的美国人
-You're an American original.
-I'm an American original.

73
00:11:32,643 --> 00:11:35,043
我真是个典型的美国人

74
00:11:35,913 --> 00:11:40,680
傻孩子，至少我不怕鬼
-Dumb kid.
-At least I'm not afraid of ghosts.

75
00:12:02,106 --> 00:12:06,372
- 孩子，保重
- 没问题，谢谢你载我一程
-Take care of yourself.
-No sweat. Thanks for the lift.

76
00:12:38,943 --> 00:12:42,538
玛西，你说水晶湖营地
Hey, Marcie. You really think
there'll be other gorgeous women...

77
00:12:42,647 --> 00:12:44,979
会不会有其他像你这样标致的妞儿？
...at Camp Crystal Lake besides yourself?

78
00:12:46,451 --> 00:12:48,180
奈德，你满脑子只有性爱吗？
-Is sex all you ever think about, Ned?
-Hey, no. No. Absolutely not.

79
00:12:48,286 --> 00:12:50,846
不…绝对不是

80
00:12:50,955 --> 00:12:53,446
有时候我会想到跟女生接吻
Sometimes I just think about kissing women.

81
00:13:18,649 --> 00:13:32,086
“欢迎光临水晶湖营地”

82
00:13:56,220 --> 00:13:58,882
- 过来帮个忙吧
- 没问题
-You wanna give me a hand over here?
-Sure.

83
00:14:00,925 --> 00:14:03,917
艾莉丝！我要把这棵树桩挖起来
Alice! I wanna get this tree stump out.

84
00:14:04,028 --> 00:14:07,429
你们过来拉这边，艾莉丝！
Get on this side, you pull
on that side. Alice!

85
00:14:07,532 --> 00:14:08,760
