Coming.

86
00:14:12,637 --> 00:14:15,470
- 好极了，我是史帝夫克斯帝
- 我是杰克
-That's great. I'm Steve Christy.
-Jack.

87
00:14:15,573 --> 00:14:17,336
- 我叫玛西
- 我是奈德鲁宾斯坦
-Marcie
-Ned Rubinstein.

88
00:14:17,441 --> 00:14:20,144
欢迎来到水晶湖营地
这是艾莉丝
Welcome to Camp Crystal Lake.
This is Alice.

89
00:14:20,144 --> 00:14:22,540
史帝夫，二号小木屋已经准备好了
Hi. Steve, Cabin B is all ready.

90
00:14:22,647 --> 00:14:25,309
比尔呢？他把船屋整理好了吗？
-Where's Bill? Cleaning out the boathouse?
-Haven't seen him in half an hour.

91
00:14:25,416 --> 00:14:27,179
我已经半个小时没看到他了

92
00:14:27,285 --> 00:14:29,719
我要他开始油漆，布兰达呢？
I wanted him to start painting. Brenda?

93
00:14:29,820 --> 00:14:32,983
- 你叫她整理射箭场
- 不，我要叫她去油漆
-Setting up the archery range.
-I'd rather she paint. Come on. Let's go.

94
00:14:33,090 --> 00:14:34,751
大家动作快

95
00:14:35,092 --> 00:14:36,923
我们不是有两个星期的时间吗？
I thought we had two weeks.

96
00:14:37,028 --> 00:14:40,794
跟我来，我带你们去换衣服
Come on. I'll show you
where you can get changed.

97
00:14:48,973 --> 00:14:52,431
- 我来帮你
- 谢谢
-Here, let me give you a hand with that.
-Thank you.

98
00:15:02,286 --> 00:15:03,344
可以了吗？
You got it?

99
