你很会画画
You draw very well.

100
00:15:28,512 --> 00:15:31,037
谢谢，可惜时间不够
Thanks. I wish I had more time to do it.

101
00:15:32,316 --> 00:15:33,715
真蠢
Oh, dummy.

102
00:15:35,186 --> 00:15:37,620
- 这是你什么时候画的？
- 昨天晚上
-When did you do this?
-Last night.

103
00:15:39,724 --> 00:15:43,683
- 我真是这个德性吗？
- 你昨晚是这样没错
-Do I really look like that?
-You did last night.

104
00:15:49,300 --> 00:15:50,995
你很有天份
You're very talented.

105
00:15:53,971 --> 00:15:55,370
你也很漂亮
You're very pretty.

106
00:15:58,109 --> 00:16:00,339
这份差事真的不适合你，对吧？
This really isn't your cup of tea, is it?

107
00:16:01,779 --> 00:16:03,246
有什么特别的原因吗？
Any particular reason?

108
00:16:04,248 --> 00:16:07,945
这是我自己的问题，跟你没有关系
It's just a problem I have.
It's nothing personal.

109
00:16:11,022 --> 00:16:13,013
- 你要走了？
- 不知道
-You wanna leave?
-I don't know. I may have to...

110
00:16:13,124 --> 00:16:16,683
