...go back to California
to straighten something out.

111
00:16:19,997 --> 00:16:23,933
别这样，再给我一次机会
Come on. Give me another chance.

112
00:16:24,301 --> 00:16:27,202
再留一个星期，帮我整顿这个地方
Stay a week.
Help get the place ready.

113
00:16:28,139 --> 00:16:34,169
到了周五你若去意仍坚，到时候我送你上车
By Friday, if you're not happy,
I'll put you on the bus myself.

114
00:16:34,412 --> 00:16:38,405
好吧，再留一个星期，到星期五
All right. Friday. I'll give it a week.

115
00:16:45,189 --> 00:16:46,656
谢了，艾莉丝
Thanks, Alice.

116
00:17:01,639 --> 00:17:04,870
比尔，史帝夫想知道是不是要更多油漆
Bill? Steve wants to know
if we need more paint.

117
00:17:04,975 --> 00:17:08,502
- 油漆够了，不过稀释剂不够
- 好，我告诉他
-Paint's all right. Need more thinner, though.
-Okay.

118
00:17:08,746 --> 00:17:10,611
艾莉丝，其他人来了吗？
-Alice. Did the others show up?
-Yeah, everybody except that girl Annie.

119
00:17:10,715 --> 00:17:13,741
大家都来了，只剩下安妮还没到

120
00:17:13,851 --> 00:17:15,375
你熬得过整个夏天吗？
-Think you're gonna last all summer?
-I don't know if I'm gonna last all week.

121
00:17:15,486 --> 00:17:18,114
我连熬一个星期的信心都没有

122
00:17:18,355 --> 00:17:21,550
