好
-I'll tell Steve about the thinner.
-Fine.

123
00:17:36,674 --> 00:17:39,165
- 你要分开列表吗？
- 对
-You want it listed separately?
-Right.

124
00:17:39,276 --> 00:17:42,473
布兰达，我要你先把射箭场整理好
Brenda, I want you to
finish the archery range.

125
00:17:42,580 --> 00:17:45,674
安妮一到就叫她到厨房工作
If Annie gets here, get her started
in the kitchen. Do your best.

126
00:17:45,783 --> 00:17:47,410
尽力而为，知道吗？

127
00:17:47,518 --> 00:17:49,486
我吃完午饭就会回来
I'll be back sometime after lunch.

128
00:17:49,687 --> 00:17:50,915
待会儿要下大雨了
It's supposed to rain like hell,
so get as much done as possible.

129
00:17:51,021 --> 00:17:53,751
你们加紧赶工，我不希望进度落后太多

130
00:18:00,331 --> 00:18:04,893
他忘了告诉我们，镇上的人称这里为血腥营地
He neglected to mention that downtown
they call this place "Camp Blood."

131
00:18:05,202 --> 00:18:09,901
搞不好这里的厕所里有蛇，湖里还有鳄鱼
Next there'll be snakes in the
outhouse and crocodiles in the lake.

132
00:18:10,007 --> 00:18:12,737
不，鳄鱼都在木屋里
No, the crocodiles are in the cabins.

133
00:18:41,539 --> 00:18:46,567
- 你疯啦？
- 我花式射箭手法更高竿
-Are you crazy?
-Wanna see my trick shot? It's even better.

134
00:18:48,445 --> 00:18:50,572
你真不可思议
I don't believe you!

135
00:18:53,751 --> 00:18:57,448
甜心，你生气时更美
You know, you're beautiful
when you're angry, sweetheart.

136
00:18:57,555 --> 00:18:58,579
- 真的吗？
- 真的
-Yeah?
-Yeah.

137
00:18:58,689 --> 00:19:01,658
你是来帮我还是来吓我的？
You come to help me or scare
me to death? You do that again...

138
00:19:01,759 --> 00:19:06,491
你敢再来这招，我就把你钉在墙上
你说这话真性感
-...l'll tack you up on the wall to dry.
-I love that sexy talk!

139
00:19:31,121 --> 00:19:34,284
嗨，我要去水晶湖营地
Hi. I'm going to Camp Crystal Lake.

140
00:19:49,406 --> 00:19:51,806
我一直都想跟孩子们共事
Guess I always wanted to
work with children.

141
00:19:51,976 --> 00:19:56,174
我讨厌听别人叫他们“小鬼”，
听起来好像小羊
I hate when people call them "kids."
Sounds like little goats.

142
00:19:56,280 --> 00:20:00,410
但我为了追求梦想，愿意不择手段
But when you've had a dream
as long as I have, you'll do anything.

143
00:20:22,606 --> 00:20:26,133
刚刚那不是通往水晶湖营地的路吗？
Hey, wasn't that the road for
Camp Crystal Lake back there?

144
00:20:31,181 --> 00:20:33,547
我们最好停车
I think we better stop.

145
00:20:36,787 --> 00:20:37,879
拜托
Please?

146
00:20:40,791 --> 00:20:44,818
停车！拜托…
Stop, please! Please! Stop!

147
00:20:45,362 --> 00:20:47,728
停车！拜托…
Please, stop!

148
00:22:11,148 --> 00:22:14,413
不！…
No. No.

149
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:17,644
不
No.

150
00:22:29,533 --> 00:22:33,867
大家一起来，往左边一点点…
All right, move it out. A little to the left.
Little to the left.

151
00:22:37,975 --> 00:22:43,675
拉出去，往左边一点点…不…
Move it out. Move it out. Okay,
little to the left. Now-- No, no.

152
00:22:44,448 --> 00:22:48,282
这样很好…很好…
Let's go. Okay. Okay. Good. Good.

153
00:23:00,364 --> 00:23:03,993
如果你是冰淇淋，你要当什么口味？
If you were a flavor of ice cream,
what would it be?

154
00:23:04,401 --> 00:23:05,868
洛基巧克力
-Rocky Road.
-Hey!

155
00:23:21,418 --> 00:23:23,978
你吃维他命C究竟是为了什么？
What's that vitamin C
stuff do for you, anyway?

156
00:23:24,088 --> 00:23:27,956
维他命C可以中和硝酸盐
Vitamin C is supposed to neutralize
the nitrates or something.

157
00:23:29,660 --> 00:23:32,857
怎么了？你是不是看到什么了？
What's the matter? Do you see something?

158
00:23:35,966 --> 00:23:37,866
没有…
No. Nothing.

159
00:23:41,839 --> 00:23:47,277
奈德！走开
Ned! Get out of here!

160
